  "panels": [
    {
      "id": 10,
      "type": "text",
      "title": "",
      "gridPos": {
        "h": 3,
        "w": 24,
        "x": 0,
        "y": 0
      },
      "options": {
        "mode": "markdown",
        "content": "## How loadgen routes traffic\n**1.** k6 sends every request to **Ollama** (no static ratio, no probability roll). **2.** Gateway tracks `ollama.in_flight`; once it hits **OLLAMA_SATURATION_THRESHOLD** (8 = NUM_PARALLEL on .240), **3.** New `target=ollama` requests get rerouted to **Claude** — IF today's running cost is below **`$20`**. **4.** When Claude's daily budget is gone, requests stay on Ollama and accept queue latency.\n_Process, not a ratio. Spillover events + budget burn appear below._"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": 20,
      "type": "row",
      "title": "🟢 Right now — what the loadgen + gateway are doing",
      "collapsed": false,
      "gridPos": {
        "h": 1,
        "w": 24,
        "x": 0,
        "y": 3
      },
      "panels": [],
      "datasource": null,
      "targets": []
    },
    {
      "id": 21,
      "type": "stat",
      "title": "Requests / sec — Ollama",
      "description": "5m rolling rate of /v1/complete calls that landed on Ollama.",
      "datasource": {
        "type": "prometheus",
        "uid": "${datasource_prom}"
      },
      "gridPos": {
        "h": 4,
        "w": 6,
        "x": 0,
        "y": 4
      },
      "fieldConfig": {
        "defaults": {
          "color": {
            "mode": "thresholds"
          },
          "decimals": 2,
          "unit": "reqps",
          "thresholds": {
            "mode": "absolute",
            "steps": [
              {
                "color": "#10B981",
                "value": null
              }
            ]
          }
        },
        "overrides": []
      },
      "options": {
        "colorMode": "value",
        "graphMode": "area",
        "justifyMode": "center",
        "orientation": "auto",
        "reduceOptions": {
          "calcs": [
            "lastNotNull"
          ],
          "fields": "",
          "values": false
        },
        "textMode": "auto",
        "wideLayout": false
      },
      "targets": [
        {
          "datasource": {
            "type": "prometheus",
            "uid": "${datasource_prom}"
          },
          "expr": "sum(rate(gen_ai_client_operation_duration_seconds_count{gen_ai_system=\"ollama\"}[5m]))",
          "instant": true,
          "refId": "A"
        }
      ]
    },
